{
 "name": "RPlog_Skeezix_s_Wife",
 "title": "Skeezix's Wife",
 "summary": "Aboard the NRV Alderaan, the grieving Captain Skeezix Calhoun, with Jessalyn Valios at his side, replays a holo confirming the death of his wife and crew as their shuttle fell into a star's gravity well; Admiral Jeralic offers his sympathies and a rescue ship. The distraught Jessalyn slips away to the MedSuite, where Luke Skywalker, the wounded Dillon, and the Horansi Kuxli are debating how to recover Han Solo from Sabbath. There a malfunctioning medical droid doses Jessalyn with a concentrated tranquilizer, and she collapses and stops breathing. Luke and a flood of would-be helpers crowd in until Doctor Alvarez and the field-medic Avalyne fight to revive her -- restarting her heart, clearing her airway, and pulling her back from a fatal overdose. Stabilized at last, an embarrassed Jessalyn whispers her apologies to Luke through Avalyne, who promises to stay with her through the night.",
